  "title": "Commis Chef",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking a driven and detail-oriented Commis Chef to support our kitchen operations. This role requires hands-on involvement in day-to-day food preparation, strong execution skills, and a commitment to excellence in a high-paced environment.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Responsibilities</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare and execute dishes from your assigned section with precision, consistency, and high presentation standards.</li>\n  <li>Assist the Chef de Partie in mise en place, service, and kitchen cleanliness.</li>\n  <li>Uphold hygiene and safety standards according to SFA and internal SOPs.</li>\n  <li>Communicate effectively with team members to ensure smooth kitchen workflow.</li>\n  <li>Participate in daily prep, service, and post-service duties with a proactive and professional attitude.</li>\n  <li>Receive and store deliveries properly, maintaining stock rotation and quality checks.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 1 years of kitchen experience in a refined or upscale restaurant setting.</li>\n  <li>Basic knife skills and understanding of mise en place systems.</li>\n  <li>Strong work ethic, adaptability, and attention to detail.</li>\n  <li>Good communication skills and ability to work well under pressure.</li>\n</ul>",
